---
By: David Seabury
Locus:
  Page: 446
  Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Spirituality
---
Spiritual victory is a living force. It reaches out and touches all who
come within its magnetic field, transforming each and every thing it
contacts. When this happens to be a human mind, it is lifted above physical
bondage, conquering tragic odds and finding joy despite the presence of
pain.
